I'm only doing this for Sakura, because there is no Christmas in Tear's world so she doesn't know this shizzle. AND I CAN SAY THIS IS WHAT SHE WAS DOING DURING MY HIATUS /o/ Tomoyo-chan: A bouquet of magnolias, and a magnolia plant that has been planted near the house. Syaoran-kun: A knitted hat, matching the scarf she gave him prior. (There are many a-reject stuffed somewhere in her room, ha.) Kero-chan: A miniature chocolate cake in the shape of Kero-chan's head. Frosting is in some parts a bit messed up. Oniichan: A knitted scarf, broken down into three warm colors. (Red/brown/red-brown shades.) A tad too long. Yukito-san: A bunch of rabbit- and moon-shaped cookies. Gingerbread, sugar, chocolate chip, each type in its own transparent wrapping. Yue-san: A dark blue ribbon for his hair, with a crescent moon stitched in yellow thread in the center, and kind of curved lines extending from it. Very very simple stitching, but a lot of time was put into it. Will-san: Also a knitted scarf, but this one is dark emerald green with cream-colored stripes. Like this. It is about the same length as Toya's, because she spaced out, and so is rather long for him. Schierke-san: A home made book mark, with pressed/dried flowers, and some flower seeds. And the following each get one (1) big sugar cookie and one (1) small sugar cookie of a Christmas shape (stars, trees, candy canes, gingerbread men, etc.) wrapped in transparent plastic and tied off with a ribbon: Cornelia-san Suzaku-san Lamperouge-san Lina-san Fiore Usagi-san Junior-san the Tsubasa cast (Sakura, Syaoran-kun, Fay-san, Kurogane-san, and Moko-chan-san) and ZETSUBOU SENSEI-SAN she will hunt you down. So yes! IC reactions here otherwise we can assume this happens off-screen~ OOC is fine, too! Damnit I typo'd "screen" FOUR TIMES IN A ROW.

Au, sorry this is late!

Um, canons! Tales of the Abyss and Card Captor Sakura are very shiny things! Also Dewprism/Threads of Fate (if you know that game THEN I AUTOMATICALLY LOVE YOU), Okami, Gundam Wing, BLOOD+, Ouran High School Host Club, Matantei Loki RAGNAROK, Full Metal Panic!, Harry Potter, pretty much anything from the Chrestomanci series by Diana Wynne Jones, or Howl's Moving Castle... (I rather dislike the movie, though. :(;;; )

I'd be most glad for anything you'd like to give! If you've got a question please feel free to ask~

Thank you very much and Merry Christmas!

:V

Name: Kinomoto Sakura Age: 11 Birthday: April 1st Height: No canon information is given, but assuming very short--4'11"-ish? Weight: Same as above, assuming around 80-90lbs. Eyes: Green Hair: Light brown Medical Info: A+++, and she's very athletic. Physical traits: Ordinary eleven-year-old girl! What's Okay To Mention Around Him/Her: Anything, I think! Well, if mentioning that she's fictional, she'll probably like...wonder how that is possible and stuff, but I don't think it would bother her. Uh, also not-safe-for-eleven-year-olds might be notsogood. Abilities: Magical: 1) Sakura Cards, 2) telling fortunes with the Cards*, 3) seeing the future in dreams.** Other: 1) Cheerleading, 2) roller-blading. * But this was only gone over once in canon, so I wouldn't really know how to do it with the rest of the cards. ** This is only if she wants to see the future, though. Sakura doesn't want to, so this will probably very rarely/never happen. Notes for the Psychics: HAPPYHAPPY JOYJOY HAPPYHAPPY JOYJOY HAP-[shot.] But yes, that's it, basically. Her mother died when she was three, but it's not a sad thing. Mm, can't really think of anything else. Can I shapeshift/bodyswap/spit at/step on/etc?: S-Sob why would you spit on Sakura? ;o; I bet if you're a giant she's easy to squash, though. UM y/y/rathernot/rathernot, just contact me before anything happens! Maim/Murder/Death: n/n/n :'( Cooking: She's okay at it, still learning. Her best recipe is hotcakes. Kissing/Hugging: WHEREISTHEKISSING Uhh okay/yes! I can't speak for your safety if Touya and/or Syaoran are around, though, sry. <:[!
